Registry Based:
    All status are posted to .Watches in Registry
Probes:
    Ping - ping host {host:, }
    Http Status Code - GET url
    Row Count (Mongo, SQL) - count
    Date range (Mongo, SQL)
    SystemD service Status - systemctl status
    Connection Success Failure - mongo,mysql
    Redis KEY - redis get
    Redis List count - redis len
    last ID change (Mongo and SQL) - latest id



Allow Node-Relationships - Graph Like
Auto Load Node props when A node is loaded.



Timeseries Data:
    /Sensors/HitCount {
        __type timeseries
        __sub_type counter / guage
    }

Push to /Sensors/HitCount with { value:, ts: }
    blueconfig will assign the id to sensor and create new
        node under HitCount

Pull On: /Sensors/HitCount { window:5m, interval:1m }
    returns 5 points with total, average, min, max and value
    get min, get max, get avg, get last value
